Package JavaDS.Trees

Class SuperTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • JavaDS.Trees.SuperTree<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of data element housed within the tree's nodes.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITree<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinaryTree
    public abstract class SuperTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITree<T>
    Main tree structure class containing shared logic for any underlying, one dimensional tree based data structure to extend from.

    Tom Esser
